__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    createAUser:
      path: /users
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Create a user
      request:
        name: UserCreate
        body:
          properties:
            name: optional<string>
            email: optional<string>
            settings: optional<UserSettings>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: User created successfully
        type: User
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              name: name
              email: email
              createdAt: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
              settings:
                theme: theme
                notifications: true
                lastModified: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
              stats:
                totalLogins: 1
                lastLoginTime: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
                accountStatus: active
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  User:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      name: optional<string>
      email: optional<nullable<string>>
      createdAt: optional<datetime>
      settings: optional<UserSettings>
      stats: optional<UserStats>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  UserSettings:
    properties:
      theme: optional<string>
      notifications: optional<boolean>
      lastModified: optional<datetime>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  UserStatsAccountStatus:
    enum:
      - active
      - suspended
      - deleted
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  UserStats:
    properties:
      totalLogins: optional<integer>
      lastLoginTime: optional<datetime>
      accountStatus: optional<UserStatsAccountStatus>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Readonly Properties API
